OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine, largely settled day
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunshine. A few morning
OL,7,Fshowers will clear southwards, leaving
OL,8,Fdry conditions. Feeling cool in brisk
OL,9,Fnortherly winds, particularly along
OL,10,Fcoastal areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear overnight skies will
OL,13,Fallow temperatures to fall away
OL,14,Fquickly, with a rural frost forming.
OL,15,FCloud will increase from the north
OL,16,Fearly on, introducing some light rain
OL,17,Fto the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
